'''Dadka Baantuuga''' ({{lang-en|Bantu people}}), sidoo kale loo yaqaano '''[[Jareer]]''', '''Gosha''', iyo '''Mushunguli''', waa [[dad|dad laga tiro badan]] yahay oo ku dhaqan koonfurta wadanka [[Soomaaliya]], meelo u dhow [[Wabiga Jubba]] iyo [[Wabiga Shabeelle]]. Dadkani waxay asal haan ka soo jeedaan [[dadka Baantuuga]] kuwaasi oo asal ahaan ku dhaqan koonfurbari qaarada [[Afrika]]. Dadka Jareerta Soomaaliya waa kuwo lagu keenay wadanka nidaam [[gumaysi]] ah.<ref>L. Randol Barker et al., ''Principles of Ambulatory Medicine'', 7 edition, (Lippincott Williams & Wilkins: 2006), p.633</ref>
